Responsive and Adaptive Layout System
Screen Size Breakpoints
Compact width < 600dp Phones portrait Single column, bottom nav Medium 600dp to 840dp Tablets portrait Two column, navigation rail Expanded width > 840dp Tablets landscape Two/three column, nav drawer

Folder Structure
res/layout/ Default — phones portrait (Compact) res/layout-w600dp/ Tablet portrait and large phones (Medium) res/layout-w840dp/ Tablet landscape (Expanded) res/layout-land/ Phone landscape override res/layout-w600dp-land/ Tablet landscape when different from w840dp

