No nested LinearLayouts where ConstraintLayout would flatten them
No android:layout_weight inside a LinearLayout inside any ScrollView variant
Resources:

Zero hardcoded dimension values — all reference @dimen/ tokens
Zero hardcoded color values — all reference ?attr/ or @color/ theme tokens
Zero hardcoded user-facing strings — all reference @string/ resources
Zero hardcoded text sizes — all reference ?attr/textAppearance* tokens
